### MY DOCKER CHEATSHEET ###

docker images -> Show docker images its can run
docker search name --> show avaible 
docker search name --size|s --> show size and files
docker pull imagename --> pull images to local
docker inspect images --> show container info
docker log container --> show container logs
docker port container --> show public ports
docker top container --> show running bin
docker stats container --> show system resources
docker rename oldcontainer newcontainer --> changes container name
docker run image-name or image-id
docker run --tty --interactive --hostname atakan ubuntu bash -> run docker images, set hostname, we will see command promp
 




